             were indicted for <rs id="t18190217-39-off231" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18190217-39-off231" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18190217-39-off231" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18190217-39-cd232" type="crimeDate">14th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190217-39-off231 t18190217-39-cd232"></join>, one handkerchief, value 2 s., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18190217-39-victim424" type="victimName">
                           James 
                           Cross
                        <interp inst="t18190217-39-victim424" type="surname" value="Cross"></interp>
